WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.202 --> 00:00:04.137
Barclays Online Banking

2
00:00:04.137 --> 00:00:06.506
How to update your personal details

3
00:00:07.073 --> 00:00:11.077
It's easy to update your personal details
with Barclays Online Banking.

4
00:00:11.077 --> 00:00:13.847
Select 'Profile' from the top of the homepage.

5
00:00:13.847 --> 00:00:17.817
Then 'Contact details' from the
'Personal details' section.

6
00:00:17.817 --> 00:00:22.389
To update your email address or phone number,
scroll down the page.

7
00:00:24.157 --> 00:00:28.661
Enter your new email address
and enter it again to confirm.

8
00:00:30.330 --> 00:00:32.399
Then tap 'Save'.

9
00:00:35.168 --> 00:00:38.538
It's the same process to update your
phone number.

10
00:00:48.748 --> 00:00:52.786
To edit your address, you’ll need your PINsentry device.

11
00:00:52.786 --> 00:00:55.288
This could either be a physical PINSentry,

12
00:00:55.288 --> 00:00:58.458
or mobile PINSentry on the Barclays app.

13
00:00:58.458 --> 00:01:00.493
Select ‘Edit Address’.

14
00:01:00.794 --> 00:01:02.729
Enter your postcode.

15
00:01:02.729 --> 00:01:05.632
Click ‘Search’ and enter your house number

16
00:01:05.632 --> 00:01:07.700
and select your new address.

17
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:11.438
If you’re happy with the details, click ‘Next’.

18
00:01:11.438 --> 00:01:14.441
Then enter the date you moved into the property.

19
00:01:14.441 --> 00:01:18.778
Please note you should only change
your address once you have moved.

20
00:01:19.245 --> 00:01:23.550
Review the details and if you’re happy, click ‘Next’.

21
00:01:23.550 --> 00:01:30.256
You’ll now need to verify it’s you making this change
by completing PINsentry authentication.

22
00:01:32.092 --> 00:01:33.493
And that's it,

23
00:01:33.493 --> 00:01:38.731
updating your personal details
made easy with Barclays Online Banking.

